# Atomic-write scratch file — transient, never commit a half-written queue.
data/escalation-queue.json.tmp
# NOTE: data/escalation-queue.json is intentionally TRACKED (not ignored) so the queue state syncs
# across the solo dev's laptops via commit/pull. Trade-offs accepted: manual sync, possible merge
# conflicts, no cross-machine dedup. In a real deployment this would be a shared queue (SQS/PubSub), not git.
